---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Magento 2 Specialist" description="Technical Magento 2 development and speed optimization.">
    <main class="pt-40 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-8 mb-20">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-6">MAGENTO 2 <br/> ENGINEERING.</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-xl">From complex migrations to custom checkout logic, we handle the technical debt others can't solve.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 py-20">
            <div class="p-8 bg-white/5 rounded-3xl border border-white/5">
                <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-4">Speed Optimization</h3>
                <p>Improving Core Web Vitals and server response times for maximum SEO impact.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 bg-white/5 rounded-3xl border border-white/5">
                <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-4">Custom Module Dev</h3>
                <p>Building proprietary logic to fit your specific business requirements.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>